alerts.description_text:
MBTA is testing PayByPhone as the only method of payment for the spaces located along Banks Pl. at Oak Grove Station. Download the free app or visit www.paybyphone.com/mbta for more information. 

Usage of PayByPhone will be license plate based (no space numbers) 

If paying cash, please park in the attended lot.

If you opt to not use PayByPhone in the parking spaces along Banks Place, a $6 parking fee invoice will be left on your Vehicle. Follow the instructions on the non-payment invoice to submit payment within 21 days to avoid penalties.
alerts.header_text: Effective Wednesday, March 11, PayByPhone is the only means of payment for Oak Grove Station's unattended parking spaces.
alerts.short_header_text: Effective Wednesday, March 11, PayByPhone is the only means of payment for Oak Grove Station's unattended parking spaces.

- Monday, April 6, 2015.
- Tuesday, April 7, 2015.
- Wednesday, April 8, 2015.
- Monday, April 27, 2015.
- Tuesday, April 28, 2015.
- Wednesday, April 29, 2015.

Wellington Station

Sullivan Station
